Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.weaponry

Class AttackPattern

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.weaponry.AttackPattern
  • public class AttackPattern
extends java.lang.Object
    An AttackPattern is a directional network of AttackModules, fully describing the working process of a Weapon.
